Interface CipherHelper

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DifferentialComparator, RecomputedOperationsCounter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AES128Helper, AES192Helper, AES256Helper, ARIA128Helper, ARIA192Helper, ARIA256Helper, ARIAHelper, BKSQ144Helper, BKSQ192Helper, BKSQ96Helper, BKSQHelper, KhazadHelper, KLEIN64Helper, KLEIN80Helper, KLEIN96Helper, KLEINHelper, LBlockHelper, LEDHelper, MCryptonHelper, PRESENT128Helper, PRESENTHelper, PRINCECoreHelper, SerpentHelper, SQUAREHelper, ThreeFishHelper, WhirlpoolCipherHelper

    public interface CipherHelper
extends DifferentialComparator, RecomputedOperationsCounter
    Marker interface, so that we can combine the functionality of DifferentialComparator and DifferentialActiveComponentsCounter in a single CipherHelper class for each cipher.
